pg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/9Dhs9immk28MrAkDLNpYZ8-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/9Dhs9immk28MrAkDLNpYZ8-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/9Dhs9immk28MrAkDLNpYZ8-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/9Dhs9immk28MrAkDLNpYZ8-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/9Dhs9immk28MrAkDLNpYZ8-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/9Dhs9immk28MrAkDLNpYZ8.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/9Dhs9immk28MrAkDLNpYZ8.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Photography by Jester Jungco and Grace Sciutto.)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#34;Ou’s inspiration happens to be my favorite painting from the National Palace Museum in Taiwan where I recently brought Baby G to visit!\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-1920-80.png.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-1600-80.png.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-1280-80.png.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-1024-80.png.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-768-80.png.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-415-80.png.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-360-80.png.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-320-80.png.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367.png\" alt=\"Photo of Christine Chiu Ou Ma Gold Gala 2025 gown.\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-1920-80.png 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-1600-80.png 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-1280-80.png 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-1024-80.png 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-768-80.png 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-415-80.png 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-360-80.png 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367-320-80.png 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367.png\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2HRsfuWFYstsTVajkbD367.png\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Photography by Jester Jungco, Grace Sciutto.)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBeijing-based couturier Ou Ma shared: \u0026#34;Designing this gown for Christine Chiu was an incredibly meaningful experience. Christine is not only a style icon but a trailblazer who continues to uplift the AAPI community with grace and strength. When I came across the Qing Dynasty painting of the camellia and plum blossom—two flowers that bloom against the cold—I immediately thought of her. Translating that imagery into a living, breathing garment felt like painting in motion. This collaboration allowed me to weave together art, culture, and personal story in the most intimate way.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RWi2HEEvnB9NPhBuLSgxhA-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RWi2HEEvnB9NPhBuLSgxhA-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RWi2HEEvnB9NPhBuLSgxhA-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RWi2HEE